description:
Hugis
<p>He was a caveman. He was hungry. He had to eat the best omelette. No normal eggs could be used for this. Where to find perfection?</p>
<ul><li>What dangers will he face on his epic quest? </li><li>Will he be able to jump across the rivers and waterfalls? </li><li>Will he get eaten instead?</li></ul>

//This is game made for our school's game project course.
//We made this to learn more about making games and programming.
//Have fun playing.


